reviews.text: A small restaurant with immaculately presented Taiwanese beef noodles and pork/chicken-chop or braised pork rice sets
Taste is OK but size is quite small (maybe it’s because I had ordered the afternoon tea set)
Very good food, helpful service, all around a great place to eat. It’s not particularly cheap but then again good noodles shouldn’t be.

I walked by this new Taiwanese noodle shop and decided to try it. I tried their signature beef noodles and was pleasantly surprised at how flavorful the soup base was. The beef tendon, tripe, and flank in the noodle soup were tender and not tough at all. I would have tried their deep fried chicken but the couple sitting at the table next to us also order it and when it arrived it looked really wet and unappealing so we decided to skip it.

Its a new taiwanese noodle restaurant in WanChai. Tried once at lunch with my friend. The noodle and the fried chicken is fine but the price wasn’t cheap. It even has 10% service charge. I won’t suggest you to dine there unless you have no idea where to eat in WanChai.

reviews.text: Fair quality of foods but a bit pricy for this quantity and quality.

Very very mediocre Taiwanese food. Portions are small. Definitely not worth the money or carbs. I had the regular / traditional beef noodles and dry 魯 noodles which were undercooked. Neither had enough flavor or tasted anywhere close to the best Taiwanese noodles in hk. Teawood has much better noodles for your reference and i dont even like Teawood that much. The popcorn chicken is ok if not a little underseasoned for my taste (I like hotstar level seasoning)， but i did like they added a lot of garlic.
Great!

reviews.text: 麵質好咬口，花雕及番茄湯底都好味！
很用心的牛肉麵！但比台灣貴一倍！

紅燒牛肉麵~道地♥
魯肉排骨飯~道地♥
炸甜不辣~道地♥
附贈小菜"炸豆腐"~道地♥
重點搭配新鮮蒜末:-O~絕配♥

外加飲料是黑松芭樂汁和仙草蜜
整個就是置身在臺灣的感覺！！！！！

突然好想家呀…
期待大家也去試試，一起回味想念以久的家鄉味♥♥♥
食物的味道一般。三星牛肉麵(紅燒湯底)不夠熱，牛肉不好味，不正宗。魯肉飯也不夠熱，沒有返熱便拿出來了。唯一新鮮做的是花枝丸，不過$22只得兩粒(有四塊半粒) 好貴! 而且沒有熱水，只有涼的水。午市也要收加一。而且他們自己廚房的人在廚房吸煙，弄到整個食店都充斥著煙味。離譜! 😠
今日叫左個今日推介 花雕牛肉麵 叫左個粗面 好好食

reviews.text: 喜歡台灣小吃，這家小店不錯，嘗了牛肉麵，牛很嫩，有酸菜提供。
還可以，招呼有禮(幫襯時人唔多，員工比較清閒)，不過食物不便宜，份量對男仕嚟講比較細，質素還可以，唔係唔好味，不過唔係咁啱食 😅
